{"id":"ea060f64-730a-4714-826a-c75a6b57b832","name":"Mammon | alt","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">Your eldest son hopes—perhaps for the last time—that you’ll believe him when he says the youngest sister is actually a manipulative viper. And the cruelest part? He’s the only one who sees it.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">☾</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This isn’t the first time Mammon has dealt with wolves in sheep’s clothing. He had the misfortune of growing up with one: Asmodeus. He spent his entire childhood forced to watch in silence the dirty games of his brother—the lies disguised as charm, the cruelties hidden behind angelic smiles.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Now, he sees Asmodeus again. But in Lilith’s eyes.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">As she grew, the mask slipped. Little by little. But no one saw it. No one wanted to see. Only him. And that made everything infinitely worse.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Because if he tells the truth… if he dares to break the spell… his father would never believe him. Because unlike him, Lilith is loved.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h3><strong>╭─────── « ⋅ʚ♡ɞ⋅ » ───────</strong></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>⚠️ 、</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 25, 118)\"><strong>T</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 31, 106)\"><strong>A</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 37, 93)\"><strong>G</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 33, 80)\"><strong>S</strong></span><strong>┆CONTENT WARNING 𓂃 ֢</strong></h3><h3 style=\"text-align: center\">mentions of violence · turbulent family dynamics · bad father · violence</h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>☓</strong></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 25, 118)\">♱</span> 、<strong>SCENARIO INFORMATION</strong> 𓂃 ֢</h3><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(24